  "rationale": "The reviewer identified that the EBO score polarity is inverted in the AUROC computation. The EBO postprocessor returns energy as confidence (higher = more ID-like), but roc_auc_score expects higher scores to predict label=1 (OOD). By negating both id_scores and ood_scores, higher values now correspond to OOD-ness, fixing the inverted AUROC values (from ~13% back to ~87%)."
